---
<BaseLayout
  title="PVC Wire & Cable Compound Products"
  description="PVC wire & cable compound product catalog: 70℃ insulation, sheath, electronic wire, plug, 105℃ heat-resistant, -40℃ cold-resistant, high-transparent, matte, modified. Each product includes application, target customers, processing method, typical specs, and inquiry points."
  locale="en"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', href: '/en/' },
    { name: 'Products', href: '/en/products/' },
  ]}
  jsonLd={{
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'ItemList',
    name: 'Xiangfa Shun PVC Wire & Cable Compound Catalog',
    itemListElement: products.map((p, i) => ({
      '@type': 'ListItem',
      position: i + 1,
      item: {
        '@type': 'Product',
        name: p.name,
        category: p.category,
        description: p.summary,
        url: `https://xfspvc.com/en/products/#${p.id}`,
        brand: { '@type': 'Brand', name: 'Xiangfa Shun' },
        manufacturer: { '@type': 'Organization', name: 'Foshan Xiangfa Shun Plastic Co., Ltd.' },
        offers: {
          '@type': 'Offer',
          availability: 'https://schema.org/MadeToOrder',
          priceCurrency: 'CNY',
          seller: { '@type': 'Organization', name: 'Foshan Xiangfa Shun Plastic Co., Ltd.' },
        },
      },
    })),
  }}
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/en/">Home</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
        <span>Products</span>
      </nav>
      <div class="section-eyebrow page-eyebrow">CATALOG · 9 CATEGORIES</div>
      <h1>PVC Wire & Cable Compound Catalog</h1>
      <p class="page-header-sub">
        Below are typical spec ranges for standard categories. Final formulation, color and performance are confirmed via mutual technical agreement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cat-nav">
        <span class="cat-nav-title">Quick Jump:</span>
        {products.map((p) => (
          <a href={`#${p.id}`} class="cat-nav-link">{p.name}</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      {products.map((p) => (
        <ProductDetail
          id={p.id}
          name={p.name}
          category={p.category}
          summary={p.summary}
          useCases={p.useCases}
          suitableCustomers={p.suitableCustomers}
          processing={p.processing}
          specs={p.specs}
          concerns={p.concerns}
          inquiryNeeds={p.inquiryNeeds}
        />
      ))}

      <div class="cta-box catalog-cta">
        <div class="catalog-cta-text">
          <h3>No perfect match?</h3>
          <p>We can develop new formulas and run small-batch trials based on your requirements. Just call or message us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="catalog-cta-actions">
          <a href={`tel:${phoneNumber}`} class="btn btn-phone btn-lg">📞 13450853338</a>
          <a href="/en/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">View Contact</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-eyebrow { margin-bottom: var(--sp-3); }

  .cat-nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: var(--sp-3) var(--sp-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xs);
  }

  .cat-nav-title {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-soft);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-right: var(--sp-2);
  }

  .cat-nav-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--color-surface-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.18s var(--ease-out);
  }

  .cat-nav-link:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .catalog-cta {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--sp-5);
    padding: var(--sp-7);
  }

  .catalog-cta h3 {
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
  }

  .catalog-cta p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
  }

  .catalog-cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .cat-nav {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .catalog-cta {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .catalog-cta-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>